case.name: DreamHack 2013 Souvenir Package
notes: Uses Collection-Rarity Tiers And Produces Only Souvenir-Quality Weapon Skins (No StatTrak, No Knives/Gloves).
Public References Indicate This Package Has Dropped Items From Multiple Collections Since Release (Dust II, Safehouse, Lake, Italy, Train, Mirage).
Known Historical Bug: R8 Revolver | Bone Mask From The Bank Collection Can Appear In The Drop Pool.
